Hannah Lee

About Me

My name is Hannah Lee, and I was born in Chicago, but currently, I live in Dublin, Ohio. In my free time, I mainly like to sleep or watch endless amounts of TV. I go to Dublin Jerome High School, where I'm involved in a lot of clubs and activities. Last year, I was did mock trial, model United Nations, student senate, junior cabinet, principal's advisory council, and the school magazine.
